text: Vladislav Koutský (born April 19, 1985) is a Czech professional ice hockey goalie. He is currently playing for HC Val Vanoise of the FFHG Division 1. Koutský made his Czech Extraliga debut playing with HC Dynamo Pardubice during the 2003-04 Czech Extraliga season. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1985 births Category:Living people Category:HC Dynamo Pardubice players Category:HC Oceláři Třinec players Category:Czech ice hockey goaltenders Category:People from Hronov
